data.description: With a newer roof and HVAC, as well as newer appliances 207 Hastings is ready to move in! You'll feel right at home in the cozy living room with a wood burning fireplace and lots of natural light.  This home offers a formal dining room which looks out to the fenced in, private back yard.  You don't have neighbors staring into your space!  The kitchen has freshly painted cabinets and new hardware.  Upstairs, you'll find your primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings, giving it a very open and spacious feel.  Two more bedrooms, a full bathroom and your laundry room are also upstairs.  Have the convenience of being within walking distance to Devon Forest Elementary School.  Shed, Washer and dryer will convey.
